        <h2>Your Rights</h2>

        <p>
          You have the right to know what personal data we have about you, for
          what purpose and how we use them, as well as the privacy notice that
          governs its processing (Access). Likewise, you may request the
          correction or updating of your personal data (Rectification); that we
          delete your personal data in situations where this is possible
          (Cancellation); as well as to oppose the processing of your personal
          data for voluntary purposes or under certain legitimate circumstances
          (Opposition) (jointly “ARCO rights“). Likewise, you may limit the use
          and disclosure of your data or revoke the consent you have given for
          its processing, when this is possible and applicable. Please note that
          the revocation of your consent could mean the end of the recruitment
          and selection process.  <br />
          To exercise any of your rights, please send your request to our Data
          Protection Officer at: zgprivacy@zillowgroup.com. <br />

          Your request must contain at least the following information: i) your
          full name, address and email address so that we can communicate the
          response to the request; ii) the document that proves your identity
          (copy of official identification) and, if applicable, personality of
          your representative (with a copy of the corresponding official
          identification); iii) a clear and precise description of the personal
          data with respect to which you are seeking to exercise any of the
          rights and the right you are exercising; iv) any document or
          information that facilitates the location of your personal data; v) in
          the event of requesting a rectification of personal data, you must
          also indicate the modifications to be made and provide the
          documentation supporting your request. <br />

          Once we receive your application, we will have 5 business days to
          review it for compliance with all requirements. If your application
          does not meet any of the above requirements, we will ask you to
          complete it within 10 business days. If you do not provide the missing
          information or documentation within the deadline, your request will be
          deemed not to have been submitted.<br />

          We will respond to your request within 20 business days after we
          receive it in full. If the request is granted, we will respond within
          15 business days. <br />

          Access to your personal data will be deemed to have been granted when
          they are made available to you, regardless of the medium or format, or
          when simple copies of your personal data are provided to you, at
          Zillow’s option.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes to the Privacy Notice</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to make changes or updates to this privacy notice
          at any time. If there are substantial modifications, we will send you
          the updated version of the privacy notice to the email address you
          have provided to us.
        </p>

        <h2>Consent</h2>

        <p>
          By providing us with your personal data and/or following the
          recruitment and selection process with us, you expressly consent to
          the processing of your personal data in accordance with this privacy
          notice.
        </p>

